The staircase opened at its bottom into a long, narrow chamber. Cody noted with interest the door in the left wall of the
room, and what appeared to be a leash lying in front of the door. He noted with rather more interest the large, rotting, and
distressing mobile dead kobold just to the left of the staircase where it entered the chamber. Fortunately, although both the
zombie kobold and Cody were quite surprised to see each other, Lulu's homicidal instincts were equal to the situation.
Without missing a beat, she lunged for the creature, causing it to awkwardly twist out of the way to avoid her snapping jaws.
